{"name": "radiumwmpfinstaller", "metadata": {"name": "RadiumWMPFInstaller", "version": "0.1.3", "classifiers": ["Environment :: Console", "Environment :: Win32 (MS Windows)", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: CPython", "Programming Language :: Python :: Implementation :: PyPy"], "home_page": "https://github.com/r3x5ur/RadiumWMPFInstaller", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["requests", "lxml", "questionary"], "summary": "RadiumWMPF installer", "upload_time": 1735267322}, "documentation": ["\r\n# RadiumWMPFInstaller\r\n\r\n> \u9002\u5408\u5728\u4f7f\u7528\u5fae\u4fe1\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u6216\u5fae\u4fe1\u5c0f\u7a0b\u5e8f\u51fa\u73b0\u5f02\u5e38\u60c5\u51b5\u7684\u65f6\u5019 <br/>\r\n> \u91cd\u65b0\u5b89\u88c5 `RadiumWMPF` <br/>\r\n> \u53ef\u4ee5\u5bf9\u5fae\u4fe1\u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u7ec4\u4ef6\u8fdb\u884c\u5347\u7ea7\u6216\u964d\u7ea7\r\n\r\n## \u5b89\u88c5\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npip install RadiumWMPFInstaller\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\r\n\r\n- \u5148\u6253\u5f00\u5e76\u767b\u5f55\u5fae\u4fe1\r\n- \u4f7f\u7528\u7ba1\u7406\u5458\u542f\u52a8\u4e00\u4e2a\u7ec8\u7aef\uff0c\u6267\u884c\u4ee5\u4e0b\u547d\u4ee4\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nRadiumWMPFInstaller\r\n```\r\n\r\n- \u9009\u62e9\u8981\u5b89\u88c5\u7684\u7248\u672c\uff0c\u4f1a\u663e\u793a\u5bf9\u5e94\u7684\u6307\u4ee4\r\n\r\n### \u5982\u4f55\u4f7f\u7528\u6307\u4ee4\r\n\r\n- \u6253\u5f00\u5fae\u4fe1\u4e3b\u9762\u677f \u6309 `CTRL+F` \u6216\u70b9\u51fb\u641c\u7d22\r\n\r\n![](images/img1.png)\r\n\r\n- \u8f93\u5165 `:showcmdwnd`\uff0c\u4f1a\u5f39\u51fa `Config Setting` \u5bf9\u8bdd\u6846\r\n\r\n![](images/img2.png)\r\n\r\n- \u5c06\u8f93\u51fa\u7684\u6307\u4ee4\u586b\u8fdb\u53bb\u540e\u70b9\u51fb\u786e\u5b9a\r\n\r\n![](images/img3.png)\r\n\r\n- \u5207\u8bb0\uff1a\u8fd9\u91cc\u8981\u7b49\u5f85\u51fa\u73b0\u5bf9\u8bdd\u6846\u540e\u518d\u91cd\u542f\u5fae\u4fe1\r\n\r\n![](images/img5.png)\r\n\r\n### \u4e5f\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u6709\u9519\u8bef\u60c5\u51b5\uff0c\u91cd\u65b0\u6267\u884c\u811a\u672c\u5373\u53ef\r\n\r\n![](images/img4.png)\r\n\r\n### \u964d\u4f4e\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef\u7248\u672c\r\n\r\n- \u5982\u679c\u6ca1\u627e\u5230\u60f3\u5b89\u88c5\u7684 `RadiumWMPF` \u7248\u672c\uff0c\u53ef\u4ee5 \r\n[\u5b89\u88c5\u65e7\u7248\u672c\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef](https://github.com/tom-snow/wechat-windows-versions/releases)\r\n\r\n\r\n- **\u5378\u8f7d\u73b0\u6709\u7248\u672c\u8bb0\u5f97\u52fe\u9009\u4e0a\u4fdd\u7559\u6570\u636e\uff0c\u9632\u6b62\u804a\u5929\u8bb0\u5f55\u4e22\u5931**\r\n![](images/img6.png)\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "rwmpf", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "rwmpf.query_wechat_version", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.query_wechat_install_path", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.get_wechat_uninstall_path", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.hex_version2str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "_str", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u7248\u672c\u53f7\u7b97\u6cd5"]}, {"name": "rwmpf.get_command", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "gray_val", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.parse_update_config_xml", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.get_system_info", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.filter_update_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.picker_version", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "rwmpf.clean_rwmpf", "asynchronous": false, "p